{"type": "article", "id": 4376, "title": "CASH CA x immun. 40L 联名背包", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-15T07:55:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233049kBLcd6qH20WwTKUZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t由日本鬼才设计师仓石一树主理的英伦时尚品牌 CASH CA 日前联手英国箱包品牌 immun. 推出了一款 40L 联名双肩背包。双方选择了 immun. 经典的 40L 背包为基础轮廓，从户外登山运动者的角色考虑，选择了深蓝色的防水帆布材料进行制作，并在底部搭配了颇具时尚色彩的格纹款羊毛物料，提供给登山爱好者一款功能性极强的背包的同时，又不失时尚与趣味。 定价 605 美元，<a href=\"http://shop.havenshop.ca/collections/new-arrivals/products/x-immun-40l-backpack/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233047ZOEz9bqMocklNVHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233047UmilcVpe3IL82XhF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330488219ukIba7GpJPc0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523304832LviXtDPJsunObw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233049NnwL7YvMoasVtiXS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}